posts.title: African Elephant
posts.content: The African elephant is the largest land animal, known for its long trunk and ivory tusks.
posts.author: Google

posts.title: Bengal Tiger
posts.author: Google
posts.content: The Bengal tiger is a powerful big cat with striking orange-and-black stripes.

posts.title: Blue Whale
posts.author: Marine Biologist
posts.content: The blue whale is the largest animal ever known to have existed, living in oceans worldwide.

posts.title: Emperor Penguin
posts.author: Penguin Enthusiast
posts.content: The emperor penguin is the tallest and heaviest of all penguin species, native to Antarctica.

posts.title: Lion
posts.author: Muhammad
posts.content: The lion is the king of the jungle.
